    h1.text-center Hello John
    h5.text-center Kansas City based Podcast about hedgehogs and flowers.
    br
    .row
      .col-xs-12.col-sm-8.col-md-6
        h5 It's Morrocan Mint, you bitch!
        p Jon and John discuss tea, hats, and muppets.
        .pcast-player
          .pcast-player-controls
            button.pcast-play
              i.fa.fa-play
              span Play
            button.pcast-pause
              i.fa.fa-pause
              span Pause
            button.pcast-rewind
              i.fa.fa-fast-backward
              span Rewind
            span.pcast-currenttime.pcast-time 00:00
            progress.pcast-progress(value='0')
            span.pcast-duration.pcast-time 00:00
            button.pcast-speed 1x
            button.pcast-mute
              i.fa.fa-volume-up
              span Mute/Unmute
          audio(src='http://s3.amazonaws.com/ShopTalk/080_rapidfire_19.mp3')
          a.pcast-download(href='http://s3.amazonaws.com/ShopTalk/080_rapidfire_19.mp3')
        a(href="#") More here.
      .col-xs-12.col-sm-4.col-md-3
        img(src="https://i.imgflip.com/hslot.jpg").img-responsive
        p Hello John KC is the best podcast in the block.
      .col-xs-12.col-md-3
        h2 Meet Your Makers
        .row
          .col-xs-4
            img(src="https://scontent-ord1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xpa1/v/t1.0-9/12036791_10103157853647939_8690026734247235835_n.jpg?oh=bf54a4aae445a14eae0c4182f85fd559&oe=56DA5606").img-responsive
          .col-xs-8
            p John Swift is the best brother in the world, and he's notorious for being extremely good at giving gifts. Any girlfriend applications can be sent to his sister, Briana.
        br
        .row
          .col-xs-4
            img(src="https://scontent-ord1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xtp1/v/t1.0-9/12208818_3094738086153_6766763569126486605_n.jpg?oh=bf85b4ddc92b990ba0ce9b5c3f23192d&oe=57159418").img-responsive
          .col-xs-8
            p Jon Chase has an unusual obsession with John Swift's mother, and has been formally diagnosed with several rare brain disorders and blood diseases. He has been cured multiple times by the power of the Lord Jesus Christ.
